twcore.core.events
Class FrequencyShipChange

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.events.SubspaceEvent
      twcore.core.events.FrequencyShipChange

public class FrequencyShipChange
extends SubspaceEvent

(S2C 0x1D) Event called when player changes ship (and possibly frequency) 

 +------------------------------+
 | Offset  Length  Description  |
 +------------------------------+
 | 0       1       Type Byte    |
 | 1       1       Ship Type    |
 | 2       2       Player ID    |
 | 4       2       Frequency    |
 +------------------------------+
Since this is the only packet associated with ship changing, getting this doesn't necessarily mean that they changed frequency too.
